WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
From Idea To Execution

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
If data is unclear, execution drifts even when the strategy looks solid on paper.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Audit one workflow stage where leadership breaks and redesign only that stage.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Choose one manager cue and track whether it changes behavior in two cycles.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
The measurable win is fewer repeated errors and clearer accountability.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Ship one focused iteration, inspect the signal, and refine the rule set.
